CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Shengfeng Development Ltd is a holding company. The firm through its subsidiaries engages in cargo warehousing, road transportation, and urban distribution. It offers contract logistics services comprising planning and designing supply chains, designing facilities, processing orders, collecting payments, managing inventories, and providing client services. Its integrated logistics solution services are comprised of three segments: B2B freight transportation; cloud storage; and value-added services.
